item.title: Help me, I am willing to pay threw paypal :)
item.dc:creator: @marcbob marcbob
item.description:
@marcbob wrote:

You don’t need to pay anyone. I will help you. Make sure you are portforwarded correctly. Also turn off your firewall. If you have done both of those things than try setting you client to connect to 0.0.0.0 and if you can do that then you didn’t portforward correctly, otherwise your just not compiling correctly.
